      <title>【数值分析】数值积分与数值微分</title>
      <link href="/2019/12/03/%E3%80%90%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%91%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86/"/>
      <url>/2019/12/03/%E3%80%90%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%91%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E7%A7%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E5%BE%AE%E5%88%86/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一数值积分">一、数值积分</h1><h2 id="插值型求积公式">插值型求积公式</h2><table><colgroup><col style="width: 5%" /><col style="width: 3%" /><col style="width: 3%" /><col style="width: 46%" /><col style="width: 41%" /></colgroup><thead><tr class="header"><th>类型</th><th>n</th><th>m</th><th>求积公式：<span class="math inline">\(\int_{a}^{b}{f(x)}dx\approx\)</span></th><th style="text-align: center;">截断误差</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>梯形</td><td>1</td><td>2</td><td><span class="math inline">\(\frac{b-a}{2}[f(a)+f(b)]\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(-\frac{(b-a)^3}{12} f^{&quot;}(\eta)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>Simpson</td><td>2</td><td>3</td><td><span class="math inline">\(\frac{b-a}{6}[f(a)+4f(\frac{a+b}{2})+f(b)]\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(-\frac{(b-a)^5}{2880} f^{(4)}(\eta)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>Cotes</td><td>4</td><td>5</td><td><span class="math inline">\(\frac{b-a}{90}[7f(a)+32f(a+h) +12f(a+2h)+32f(a+3h)+7f(b)]\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(-\frac{2(b-a)}{945} (\frac{b-a}{4})^6 f^{(6)}(\eta)\)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>Cotes系数</strong></p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">n</th><th style="text-align: right;"><span class="math inline">\(c^{n}_i\)</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">1</td><td style="text-align: right;"><span class="math inline">\([1\ \ \ 1]/2\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">2</td><td style="text-align: right;"><span class="math inline">\([1\ \ \ 4 \ \ \ 1]/6\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;">3</td><td style="text-align: right;"><span class="math inline">\([1\ \ \ 3 \ \ \ 3 \ \ \ 1]/8\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;">4</td><td style="text-align: right;"><span class="math inline">\([7\ \ \ 32 \ \ \ 12 \ \ \ 32 \ \ \ 7]/90\)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="复化求积公式区间数n">复化求积公式（区间数：<span class="math inline">\(n\)</span>）</h2><table><colgroup><col style="width: 8%" /><col style="width: 2%" /><col style="width: 44%" /><col style="width: 44%" /></colgroup><thead><tr class="header"><th>类型</th><th style="text-align: center;">节点</th><th style="text-align: center;">求积公式：<span class="math inline">\(\int_{a}^{b}{f(x)}dx\approx\)</span></th><th style="text-align: center;">截断误差</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>复化梯形</td><td style="text-align: center;">n+1</td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(T_n(f)=\frac{h}{2}{[f(a)+2\sum_{i=1}^{n-1}f(x_i)+f(b)]}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(E_{T_n}(f)=-\frac{b-a}{12}h^2f^{&quot;}(\eta)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>复化Simpson</td><td style="text-align: center;">2n+1</td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(S_n(f)=\frac{h}{6}{[f(a)+2\sum_{i=1}^{n-1}f(x_i)+4\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}f(x_{i+\frac{1}{2}})+f(b)]}\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(E_{S_n}(f)=-\frac{b-a}{2880}h^4f^{(4)}(\eta)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>复化Cotes</td><td style="text-align: center;">3n+1</td><td style="text-align: center;"></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(E_{C_n}(f)=-\frac{2(b-a)}{945}(\frac{h}{4})^6f^{(6)}(\eta)\)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>误差的后验估计方法</strong>：区间逐次分半，自适应步长</p><table><colgroup><col style="width: 15%" /><col style="width: 84%" /></colgroup><thead><tr class="header"><th>类型</th><th style="text-align: center;">重要关系</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>复化梯形</td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(I(f)\approx T_{2n}(f)+\frac{1}{3}[T_{2n}(f)-T_{n}(f)]=S_n(f)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>复化Simpson</td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(I(f)\approx S_{2n}(f)+\frac{1}{15}[S_{2n}(f)-S_{n}(f)]=C_n(f)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>复化Cotes</td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(I(f)\approx C_{2n}(f)+\frac{1}{63}[C_{2n}(f)-C_{n}(f)]S_n(f)=R_n(f)\)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p>计算截至条件：<span class="math inline">\(|T_{2n}(f)-T_{n}(f)| \leq \varepsilon\)</span></p><h2 id="romberg求积算法">Romberg求积算法</h2><ul><li>利用补步长折半的校正方法可以提高求积公式的误差阶</li><li>步长折半的复化Cotes公式即为Romberg求积公式</li></ul><h2 id="外推技巧">外推技巧</h2><p><span class="math display">\[Q_1^{*}(h)=\frac{1}{1-2^{b_1}}Q^*(h)+\frac{-2^{b_1}}{1-2^{b_1}}Q^*(\frac{h}{2})\]</span></p><ul><li>利用两个低阶近似的线性组合何以得到一个更为高阶的近似</li><li>其中，<span class="math inline">\(b_1\)</span>为原低阶近似的误差阶</li></ul><h2 id="gauss型求积公式">Gauss型求积公式</h2><ul><li>Gauss型求积公式是插值型，也是代数精度最高的求积公式</li><li>求积节点的个数为<span class="math inline">\(n+1\)</span>，但其代数精度能够达到<span class="math inline">\(2n+1\)</span></li><li>某一组节点为Gauss点的【充要】条件为：</li></ul><p><span class="math display">\[\int_{a}^{b}{\omega_{n+1}(x)p(x)\rho(x)dx=0}\]</span></p><p>即，<span class="math inline">\(\omega_{n+1}=(x-x_0)(x-x_1)\dots(x-x_n)\)</span>与不超过<span class="math inline">\(n\)</span>次的多项式<span class="math inline">\(p(x)\)</span><strong>带权正交</strong>。</p><ul><li>Gauss型求积公式都是稳定的</li><li>截断误差：</li></ul><p><span class="math display">\[E_n(f)=\frac{f^{(2n+2)}(\eta)}{(2n+2)!}\int_{a}^{b}{[\omega_{n+1}(x)]^2\rho(x)}dx\]</span></p><ul><li>常用的Gauss型求积公式<ul><li>Gauss-Legendre 公式</li><li>Gauss-Chebyshev 公式</li><li>Gauss-Laguerre 公式</li><li>Gauss-Hermite 公式</li></ul></li></ul><hr /><h1 id="二数值微分">二、数值微分</h1><h2 id="插值型求导公式">插值型求导公式</h2><ol type="1"><li>两点数值微分公式<ul><li>$ f'(x_0)=[f(x_1)-f(x_0)]-f^{"}(_1)$</li><li>$ f'(x_1)=[f(x_1)-f(x_0)]+f^{"}(_2)$</li></ul></li><li>三点数值微分公式<ul><li>$ f'(x_0)=[-3f(x_0)+4f(x_1)-f(x_2)]+f^{(3)}(_1)$</li><li>$ f'(x_1)=[f(x_2)-f(x_0)]-f^{(3)}(_2)$</li><li>$ f'(x_3)=[f(x_0)-4f(x_1)+3f(x_2)]+f^{(3)}(_3)$</li></ul></li></ol><h2 id="taylor级数展开法">Taylor级数展开法</h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
