      <title>【矩阵论】广义逆矩阵</title>
      <link href="/2019/11/27/%E3%80%90%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%91%E5%B9%BF%E4%B9%89%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/"/>
      <url>/2019/11/27/%E3%80%90%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%91%E5%B9%BF%E4%B9%89%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr /><hr /><h1 id="一广义逆矩阵的概念">一、广义逆矩阵的概念</h1><ol type="1"><li>四个Penrose方程：设<span class="math inline">\(A\in C^{m\times n}\)</span>,<span class="math inline">\(X\in C^{n\times m}\)</span>，有<ul><li><ol type="1"><li><span class="math inline">\(AXA=A\)</span></li></ol></li><li><ol start="2" type="1"><li><span class="math inline">\(XAX=X\)</span></li></ol></li><li><ol start="3" type="1"><li><span class="math inline">\((AX)^H=AX\)</span></li></ol></li><li><ol start="4" type="1"><li><span class="math inline">\((XA)^H=XA\)</span></li></ol></li></ul></li><li>常用的广义逆<ul><li>{1}逆：仅满足条件（1）</li><li>Moore-Penrose逆：满足所有条件，记为<span class="math inline">\(A^+\)</span>，也称加号逆</li></ul></li><li>重要定理<ul><li>矩阵的Moore-Penrose逆存在且唯一，从而所有类型（共15类）的广义逆矩阵均存在</li><li>只要A不可逆，则除Moore-Penrose逆以外的其他所有逆均不唯一</li></ul></li></ol><hr /><h1 id="二1逆">二、{1}逆</h1><h2 id="求解步骤">求解步骤：</h2><ul><li>step1：化Hermite标准形，求变换阵<span class="math inline">\(S\)</span>，<span class="math inline">\(P\)</span> ；</li><li>step2：引入参数矩阵：<span class="math inline">\(L=[ \ \alpha \ , \beta \ , \ ...]\)</span> 等；</li><li>step3：代入公式：<span class="math inline">\(X=P\begin{bmatrix}I_r&amp;O\\O&amp;L\end{bmatrix}S\)</span>；</li><li>step4：若令其中的参数全部为0，则可以进一步的得到矩阵的<span class="math inline">\(\{1，2\}\)</span>逆。</li></ul><h1 id="三moore-penrose逆">三、Moore-Penrose逆</h1><h2 id="求解步骤-1">求解步骤：</h2><p>利用满秩分解求解矩阵的<span class="math inline">\(A^+\)</span></p><ul><li>step1：求满秩分解<span class="math inline">\(A=FG\)</span></li><li>step2：代入公式<span class="math inline">\(A^+=G^H(GG^H)^{-1}(F^HF)^{-1}F^H\)</span></li></ul><p>特殊的：</p><ul><li>当A为行满秩时：<span class="math inline">\(A^+=A^H(AA^H)^{-1}\)</span></li><li>当A为列满秩时：<span class="math inline">\(A^+=(A^HA)^{-1}A^H\)</span></li></ul><h1 id="四广义逆矩阵的应用">四、广义逆矩阵的应用：</h1><h2 id="线性方程组的求解">线性方程组的求解</h2><h3 id="利用a1">1）利用<span class="math inline">\(A\{1\}\)</span>​</h3><ul><li>可解性（充要）：<span class="math inline">\(AA^{(1)}b=b\)</span></li><li>通解：<span class="math inline">\(x=A^{(1)}b+(I-A^{(1)}A)y \ \ ,\  \forall y\in C^n\)</span></li></ul><h3 id="利用a">2）利用<span class="math inline">\(A^+\)</span></h3><ul><li>可解性（充要）：<span class="math inline">\(AA^+b=b\)</span></li><li>通解：<span class="math inline">\(x=A^+b+(I-A^+A)y \ \ ,\  \forall y\in C^n\)</span></li></ul><p>利用Morre-Penrose逆求解线性方程组<span class="math inline">\(Ax=b\)</span>时可以得到下整齐的结论：</p><ul><li>有解（相容）的充分必要条件为<span class="math inline">\(AA^+b=b\)</span>；</li><li><span class="math inline">\(A^+b+(I-A^+A)y \ \ ,\  \forall y\in C^n\)</span>表示相容方程组的通解，或者矛盾方程组的全部最小二乘解；</li><li><span class="math inline">\(x_0=A^+b\)</span>是相容方程组的唯一极小范数解，或是矛盾方程组的唯一极小范数最小二乘解。</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>【数值分析】插值</title>
      <link href="/2019/11/26/%E3%80%90%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%91%E6%8F%92%E5%80%BC/"/>
      <url>/2019/11/26/%E3%80%90%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%91%E6%8F%92%E5%80%BC/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr /><hr /><h1 id="插值问题">插值问题</h1><ul><li>插值问题主要分为内插法和外插法，本文主要讨论内插法</li><li>插值问题的存在星河唯一性（多项式插值、拉格朗日插值、牛顿插值、等距节点插值）</li><li>常用的插值方式有：三角插值、有理插值、多项式插值</li><li>不同构造方法的余项都相同（唯一性）</li></ul><hr /><h1 id="多项式插值">多项式插值</h1><h2 id="插值多项式">插值多项式</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(P^n=|\varphi (x)|\varphi (x)=\sum_{ i=0 }^{n} { a_i x^i }\)</span></p><p>其中：多项式系数由下列范德蒙得方程组求得 （非奇异、存在病态问题）</p><p><span class="math inline">\(\left[\begin{array}{ccccc}{1} &amp; {x_{0}} &amp; {x_{0}^{2}} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {x_{0}^{n}} \\ {1} &amp; {x_{1}} &amp; {x_{1}^{2}} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {x_{1}^{n}} \\ {\cdots} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {\cdots} \\ {1} &amp; {x_{n}} &amp; {x_{n}^{2}} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {x_{n}^{n}}\end{array}\right]\left[\begin{array}{c}{a_{0}} \\ {a_{1}} \\ {a_{2}} \\ {\vdots} \\ {a_{n}}\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{c}{f\left(x_{0}\right)} \\ {f\left(x_{1}\right)} \\ {f\left(x_{2}\right)} \\ {\vdots} \\ {f\left(x_{n}\right)}\end{array}\right]\)</span></p><h2 id="插值余项">插值余项</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(R_{n}(x)=f(x)-\varphi(x)=\frac{f^{(n+1)}(\xi)}{(n+1) !} \omega_{n+1}(x)\)</span></p><p><span class="math inline">\(\left|R_{n}(x)\right| \leq \frac{M_{n+1}}{(n+1) !}\left|\omega_{n+1}(x)\right|\)</span> （导函数有界）</p><p>其中</p><p><span class="math inline">\(\omega_{n+1}(x)=\prod_{i=0}^{n}\left(x-x_{i}\right)\)</span></p><h2 id="推论">推论</h2><ul><li>当<span class="math inline">\(f(x)\)</span>为不超过n次的多项式时，<span class="math inline">\(f(x)=\varphi (x)\)</span></li><li>节点距离<span class="math inline">\(x\)</span>越近，一般插值误差越小</li></ul><hr /><h1 id="拉格朗日插值">拉格朗日插值</h1><h2 id="插值条件">插值条件</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(l_{i}\left(x_{j}\right)=\delta_{i j} \stackrel{\Delta}{=}\left\{\begin{array}{ll}{1} &amp; {j=i} \\ {0} &amp; {j \neq i}\end{array}, \quad j=0,1,2, \cdots, n\right.\)</span> （线性无关）</p><h2 id="插值基">插值基</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(l_i (x)=\frac{\omega_{n+1}(x)}{\left(x-x_{i}\right) \omega_{n+1}^{\prime}\left(x_{i}\right)}\)</span></p><h2 id="插值多项式-1">插值多项式</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(L_{n}(x) \stackrel{\Delta}{=} \sum_{i=0}^{n} f\left(x_{i}\right) l_{i}(x)=\sum_{i=0}^{n} f\left(x_{i}\right) \frac{\omega_{n+1}(x)}{\left(x-x_{i}\right) \omega_{n+1}^{\prime}\left(x_{i}\right)}\)</span></p><h2 id="插值余项-1">插值余项</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(R_{n}(x)=f(x)-L_{n}(x)=\frac{f^{(n+1)}(\xi)}{(n+1) !} \omega_{n+1}(x)\)</span></p><p><span class="math inline">\(\left|R_{n}(x)\right|=\left|f(x)-L_{n}(x)\right| \leq \frac{M_{n+1}}{(n+1) !}\left|\omega_{n+1}(x)\right|\)</span></p><h2 id="应用">应用</h2><ul><li>插值（采用列表的方法一目了然）</li><li>反插值（单值性条件：被插函数单调连续）</li></ul><h2 id="特点">特点</h2><ul><li>形式对称</li><li>通常用于理论分析</li><li>当增加插值节点时，计算不方便</li></ul><h1 id="牛顿插值">牛顿插值</h1><h2 id="差商">差商</h2><p>重要工具：差商表</p><p>差商的性质：对称性，与导数的关系</p><h2 id="插值公式">插值公式</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(\begin{aligned} N_{n}(x)=&amp; f\left(x_{0}\right)+f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}\right]\left(x-x_{0}\right)+f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}, x_{2}\right]\left(x-x_{0}\right)\left(x-x_{1}\right)+\\ &amp;\cdots+f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}, \cdots, x_{n}\right]\left(x-x_{0}\right)\left(x-x_{1}\right) \cdots\left(x-x_{n-1}\right) \end{aligned}\)</span></p><p>加入节点后：</p><p><span class="math inline">\(N_{n+1}(x)=N_{n}(x)+f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}, \cdots, x_{n}\right] \omega_{n+1}(x)\)</span></p><h2 id="余项">余项</h2><p>插值型：<span class="math inline">\(R_n (x)=f\left[x,x_{0}, x_{1}, \cdots, x_{n}\right] \omega_{n+1}(x)\)</span></p><p>导数型：<span class="math inline">\(R_{n}(x)=f(x)-N_{n}(x)=\frac{f^{(n+1)}(\xi)}{(n+1) !} \omega_{n+1}(x)\)</span></p><p>导数与差商的关系：<span class="math inline">\(f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}, \cdots, x_{k}\right]=\frac{f^{(k)}(\xi)}{k !}\)</span></p><h2 id="特点-1">特点</h2><ul><li>有利于节点数的增加</li><li>对函数的光滑性要求高</li><li>需要估计导函数的最值</li><li>保守</li></ul><h1 id="等距节点插值">等距节点插值</h1><p>当节点等距分布时简化Newton插值公式：<span class="math inline">\(x_{i}=a+i h \quad(i=0,1, \cdots, n) \quad h=\frac{b-a}{n}&gt;0\)</span></p><h2 id="常用差分算子">常用差分算子</h2><p>向前差分：<span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{array}{c}{\Delta f(x)=f(x+h)-f(x)} \\ {\Delta^{m} f(x)=\Delta\left(\Delta^{m-1} f(x)\right)}\end{array}\right.\)</span></p><p>向后差分：<span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{array}{c}{\nabla f(x)=f(x)-f(x-h)} \\ {\nabla^{m} f(x)=\nabla\left(\nabla^{m-1} f(x)\right)}\end{array}\right.\)</span></p><p>恒等算子：<span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{array}{}{I f(x)=f(x)} \\ {I^{m} f(x)=I\left(I^{m-1} f(x)\right)}\end{array}\right.\)</span></p><p>位移算子：<span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{array}{}{E f(x)=f(x+h)} \\ {E^{s} f(x)=f(x+s h)}\end{array}\right.\)</span></p><p>中心差分：<span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{array}{}{\delta f(x)=f\left(x+\frac{h}{2}\right)-f\left(x-\frac{h}{2}\right)} \\ {\delta^{m} f(x)=\delta\left(\delta^{m-1} f(x)\right)}\end{array}\right.\)</span></p><p>差分算子的重要性质：</p><ul><li><span class="math inline">\(\Delta=E-I\)</span></li><li><span class="math inline">\(\nabla=I-E^{-1}\)</span></li><li><span class="math inline">\(\delta=E^{1 / 2}-E^{-1 / 2}\)</span></li></ul><p>差分与差商的关系：</p><p><span class="math inline">\(f\left[x_{0}, x_{1}\right]=\frac{f\left(x_{1}\right)-f\left(x_{0}\right)}{x_{1}-x_{0}}=\frac{\Delta f\left(x_{0}\right)}{1 \cdot h}\)</span></p><h2 id="插值公式-1">插值公式</h2><p>向前：</p><p><span class="math inline">\(N_{n}(a+t h)=f\left(x_{0}\right)+\sum_{k=1}^{n} \frac{\Delta^{k} f\left(x_{0}\right)}{k !} t(t-1) \cdots(t-k+1)\)</span></p><p><span class="math inline">\(N_{2}\left(x_{0}+t h\right)=f\left(x_{0}\right)+\frac{\Delta f\left(x_{0}\right)}{1 !} t+\frac{\Delta^{2} f\left(x_{0}\right)}{2 !} t(t-1)\)</span></p><p>向后：</p><p><span class="math inline">\(N_{n}(b+t h)=f\left(x_{n}\right)+\sum_{k=1}^{n} \frac{\nabla^{k} f\left(x_{n}\right)}{k !} t(t+1) \cdots(t+k-1)\)</span></p><h1 id="hermite插值">Hermite插值</h1><h2 id="插值条件-1">插值条件</h2><p><span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{array}{l}{H_{2 n+1}\left(x_{i}\right)=f\left(x_{i}\right)} \\ {H_{2 n+1}^{\prime}\left(x_{i}\right)=f^{\prime}\left(x_{i}\right)}\end{array} i=0,1,2, \cdots, n\right. （唯一性）\)</span></p><h2 id="插值基-1">插值基</h2><h2 id="插值多项式-2">插值多项式</h2><h2 id="余项-1">余项</h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
